  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 791249b4e3ab1d14db97e9b040eb66af, type: 3}
  m_Name: New Dialogue Obj
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Helloooo my child, my name is Felix and this is the real world.
  - Our owner is being haunted, and to free him you need to get rid of the ghosts
    in the dream world.
  - "This house is just a simulation of what you\u2019ll find when things get real."
  - As shown on screen, the game environment contains various items, each with its
    own function.
  - 'Your main objective is to find the Capture Bucket, the only item in the game
    that can permanently get rid of ghosts. (Note: in the astral plane, it is an
    unnamed magical bottle.)'
  - When you collect this item, the ghost runs away and in this world you can capture
    it on touch, however in the astral reign you need to press "E" while aiming at
    it.
  - "This item normally lasts only a few seconds, but since you\u2019re a noob, here
    it lasts forever (hehehe)."
  - Other items can help you on your journey, but in the dream reign both enemies
    and items have a different appearance.
  - "I almost forgot \u2014 when you pick up the yarn ball, press the \u2018right
    mouse button\u2019 to shoot it."
  - Shoot the roomba 3 times and it will be temporarily paralyzed.
  - "I wanted it to be \u2018ESC\u2019 but the game kept closing for some reason
    ;________;)"
  - Now go ahead and capture the that roomba basterd for me.
  - "If you hhave any questions, don\xB4t call me"
